{
  "stem": "7598.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You don't go anywhere near them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because what they could've done is taken the jacket off our shoulders or whatever.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Anyway, that somehow didn't happen anyway.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We got onto an ordinary train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the frontier between Belgium and France had been changed from where it was to the Somme River, which actually makes more sense because a river is a better space for a frontier.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the frontier was renamed [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Why, I don't quite know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But one of the difficult things we had to do was to cross the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We got onto a normal train, and we got off just before the frontier.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We waited for quite a long time at the station.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And then when it was dark, we all-- we were told-- like a herd, we did what we were told.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We knew then that it was all or nothing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We walked for a few miles along the railroad lines.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And there we stopped.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "At that point, we were given instructions that a certain train-- and we, we would be told which one it was-- would slow down.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And a couple doors would open in cattle wagons.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And this is where we had to jump onto-- that the train would be very slow but would still be moving.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And that train would then take us to Paris.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] The French railway workers, by the way, were very good.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "A lot of them were members of the resistance.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But they liked the money as well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "So although they were paid, it was a mixture of both.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "They, they would be helping-- I say the Jews because I think mainly Jews tried to get out.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "There were some non-Jews.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But they were really quite pleasant.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Anyway, this said train arrived and slowed down.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
